data.description: No need to wait to build...this 2 year old Emerald floor plan is ready to call home! This 3-car garage home has 5 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms. The owner's suite includes a walk-in closet and large bathroom with dual sinks, shower with seat and private toilet room. An airy, open layout showcases the kitchen, the dining room, and the great room. Kitchen has a center island with breakfast bar, sink and granite counter tops. Washer and dryer included! Backyard ready to add your special touch!
